DISCLAIMER:

Archie Guardian is a security monitoring tool. While it aims to provide
transparent, local threat detection, users are responsible for:

1. Understanding the limitations of the system
2. Running it alongside traditional security tools
3. Keeping their operating system and dependencies updated
4. Reviewing audit logs and alerts regularly

The authors assume no liability for missed threats, false positives, or any
damage resulting from use or misuse of this software.

Use at your own risk. We recommend this tool for developers, security
researchers, and privacy-conscious users who understand the threat model
outlined in the technical documentation.
